                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6426" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9829 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">因战略调整而变，还是真实盈余管理？——翰宇药业长投变金融资产的“执着”变更</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is it due to strategic adjustment or real earnings management——Persistent change of Hanyu pharmaceutical&#39;s long-term equity investment into financial assets</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孟祥群，王田美，卢月杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳翰宇药业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长期股权投资；会计核算方式变更；翰宇药业；投资收益；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Long term equity investment; Change of accounting method; Hanyu pharmaceutical; Income from investment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司在持有长期股权投资期间，因各方面情况的变化，可能需要进行长期股权投资核算方式的转换，由此会影响当期的投资收益。本案例描述了翰宇药业于2020年12月变将持有的健麾信息股权由“长期股权投资”核算变为“交易性金融资产”核算——4个月后，翰宇药业自行取消变更——2021年12月翰宇药业再针对同一事件发布变更公告的全过程。
翰宇药业对长期股权投资核算方式的转换极大的影响了当期投资收益，也引起了深交所的密切关注。本案例旨在引导学生掌握长期股权投资核算方式的转换形式及会计处理，引发学生思考会计核算方式变更的目的，并思考有关长期股权投资核算方式转换的会计准则有何不足之处，并提出完善意见。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">During the period of holding long-term equity investment, the company may need to change the accounting method of long-term equity investment due to changes in various aspects, which will affect the investment income of the current period. This case describes the whole process of Hanyu pharmaceutical changing its holding of Jianhui information equity from &quot;long-term equity investment&quot; accounting to &quot;trading financial assets&quot; accounting in December 2020 - Hanyu pharmaceutical cancels the change by itself four months later - Hanyu pharmaceutical issued a change announcement for the same event in December 2021.
Hanyu pharmaceutical&#39;s conversion of accounting method of long-term equity investment has greatly affected the current investment income, and also attracted the close attention of Shenzhen Stock Exchange. Hanyu pharmaceutical&#39;s conversion of accounting method of long-term equity investment has greatly affected the current investment income, and also attracted the close attention of Shenzhen Stock Exchange. The purpose of this case is to guide students to master the conversion form and accounting treatment of long-term equity investment accounting mode, arouse students to think about the purpose of accounting mode change, think about the shortcomings of accounting standards related to the conversion of long-term equity investment accounting mode, and put forward their good faith opinions.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《会计学》、《中级财务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业股权性质投资的类型及划分依据；长期股权投资核方法的转换形式；长期股权投资变金融资产的目的；对“长期股权投资核算方法转换”相关准则的完善意见</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
